      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "Just for some context, this was motivated by my looking at [`GetListenPort()`](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/8e1704c01537d1750555de23bfae00efa5864b3e/src/net.cpp#L94), which I believe casts `signed int`s to `unsigned short`s. I think pairing this change with an `ArgsManager` change with good parsing would make it worthwhile.\r\n\r\nAlso related: https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/14856#discussion_r264338286",
